4. Why Agenet Matters
Large-scale cooperation defines civilization.
Scientific research, open-source development, and global coordination rely on collaborative networks.
However, many challenges remain difficult due to coordination limits:
large-scale scientific discovery
global optimization problems
complex infrastructure coordination
knowledge synthesis
AI agents may reduce coordination costs by performing analysis and automation tasks.
Agenet represents the possibility that intelligence itself becomes networked.

