Stage 2 — Human-Agent Collaboration
AI agents assist human decision making.
Stage 3 — Hybrid Intelligence
Human judgment merges with AI capabilities.
Stage 4 — Autonomous Agent Ecosystems
Autonomous agents operate alongside humans.

